<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.vmt.org/">Virginia Museum of Transportation</a> located in Roanoke, VA</li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://finance.groups.yahoo.com/group/southern_railway/">Southern Railway Yahoo Group</a> a Yahoo group for former employees, railfans and modelers of the Southern Railway</li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://finance.groups.yahoo.com/group/Norfolk_Southern/">Norfolk Southern Yahoo Group</a> a Yahoo group for current happenings of Norfolk Southern Railway</li>
</ul>
